node.text:
Happy Wednesday 💜 so happy that Ive been staying consistent with my work outs and my meals. I felt like I was losing my passion for fitness and training for a while and finding a routine that worked for me and that I looked forward to was the spark I needed. Remember fitness is not one size fits all, fitness is not one certain body type lol r way of training, it’s moving your body and enjoying it. 

•••••••••••

Wearing @forthepeach doing a huge giveaway soon 👁👄👁 what do you think I’m giving away? 👇🏼

node.text:
Ready to get one day closer to my goals tomorrow ✨👏🏼 it’s so crazy how bad my body dysmorphia is sometimes, I took this picture a few weeks ago and deleted it immediately. Today I was going through my recently deleted and came across it and thought to myself wtf!? It took me such a long time to get to a place of acceptance for myself and my body and it gets better. If you’re experiencing this, it gets better. It helps me when I talk to my therapist and my loved ones and also letting myself feel the emotions I feel and being kind and gentle to myself. I’m here if any of you ever wanna talk 💜 

••••••••

Wearing @forthepeach

Happy Wednesday ✨ this circuit destroyed my abs omg, give it a try and let me know if you like it! 

••••••••••••

My workout app and merch are available on the link in my bio ✨
